data.description: Looking for a home that has it all? This stunning 4 bedroom, 3 bath oasis is the epiphany of southern living. With 2 en-suites and a game room, there's plenty of room for everyone to spread out and relax. Relax in the sparkling pool and hot tub for year-round fun, you'll never want to leave home. With all the amenities the city has to offer. Don't miss out on this great investment. USDA Eligible 100% Financing Available
